        <para id="id15655812"/>
        <para id="id15655816">BRAIN-TEASER!</para>
        <para id="id22644958">Francois has a bag of marbles. If he divides them into groups of 4, 2are left over. If he divides them into groups of 5, 1 is left over. How many marbles can there be in his bag? Could you write down 5 possible answers in the bag?</para>
