    <section id="id8696334">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id21883451"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis> The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id15746048"><emphasis effect="bold">Assessment Standard 1.12:</emphasis> We know this when the learner recognises, describes and uses:</para>
      <para id="id21742615"><emphasis effect="bold">1.12.1:</emphasis> divisibility rules for 2, 5, 10, 100 and 1 000.</para>
